### ========================================
### STAFF API TESTS
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000/api/staff
### ========================================

### 1. Get all staff (with pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff?page=1&limit=10

###

### 2. Get all staff with filters (position filter)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff?position=Manager&is_active=true

###

### 3. Get staff statistics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff/stats

###

### 4. Create new staff (with account)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "SecurePass123!",
  "email": "john.doe@minimarket.com",
  "full_name": "John Doe",
  "phone": "+84901234567",
  "address": "123 Main Street, District 1, HCMC",
  "date_of_birth": "1990-05-15",
  "position": "Sales Associate",
  "employment_type": "Full-time",
  "annual_salary": 180000000,
  "hire_date": "2024-01-15",
  "notes": "Experienced retail worker"
}

###

### 5. Create another staff (Manager)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "jane_manager",
  "password": "ManagerPass456!",
  "email": "jane.manager@minimarket.com",
  "full_name": "Jane Smith",
  "phone": "+84907654321",
  "address": "456 Business Ave, District 3, HCMC",
  "date_of_birth": "1985-08-20",
  "position": "Store Manager",
  "employment_type": "Full-time",
  "annual_salary": 360000000,
  "hire_date": "2023-06-01",
  "notes": "5 years management experience"
}

###

### 6. Get single staff by ID (replace {staffId} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff/674cf1234567890abcdef123

###

### 7. Get staff by account ID (replace {accountId} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff/account/674cf1234567890abcdef124

###

### 8. Update staff
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/staff/674cf1234567890abcdef123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "John Doe Jr.",
  "phone": "+84901234999",
  "position": "Senior Sales Associate",
  "annual_salary": 220000000,
  "notes": "Promoted to senior position"
}

###

### 9. Search staff by name
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff?search=John&page=1&limit=10

###

### 10. Filter staff by employment type
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff?employment_type=Full-time&is_active=true

###

### 11. Get staff sorted by creation date (newest first)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/staff?sort=-createdAt&limit=5

###

### 12. Soft delete staff (deactivate)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/staff/674cf1234567890abcdef123

###

### 13. Activate staff
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/staff/674cf1234567890abcdef123/activate

###

### 14. Permanently delete staff (USE WITH CAUTION!)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/staff/674cf1234567890abcdef123/permanent

###

