### TEST SCENARIOS
### ========================================

### Scenario 1: Create staff with minimal info
POST http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "minimal_staff",
  "password": "Pass123!",
  "email": "minimal@minimarket.com",
  "position": "Cashier"
}

###

### Scenario 2: Try to create staff with duplicate username (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john_doe",
  "password": "AnotherPass123!",
  "email": "another@minimarket.com",
  "position": "Cashier"
}

###

### Scenario 3: Try to create staff with duplicate email (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "unique_username",
  "password": "Pass123!",
  "email": "john.doe@minimarket.com",
  "position": "Cashier"
}

###

### Scenario 4: Create staff without required fields (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/staff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "No Username Staff"
}

###

